'''Jyri Aalto''' (born 11 July 1969) is a Finnish [[badminton]] player. He competed in the [[Badminton at the 2000 Summer Olympics – Men's singles|singles event]] at the [[2000 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="SportsRef">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/aa/jyri-aalto-1.html |title=Jyri Aalto Olympic Results |accessdate=28 November 2017}}</ref>

