{{portal|Evolutionary biology}}
*[[Biomimicry]], which includes biologically inspired engineering
*[[Projectile use by living systems]], another adaptation commonly associated with human technology
*[[Robot locomotion]], in which locomotive issues faced by living systems are addressed in a technological context
*[[Suspension (vehicle)]], a key element in the design of wheeled systems

